Invocation Name: hound hub
des:
Hound Hub quickly lets dog owners book appointments for their beloved pets! You can choose between services such as veterinary care, dog walking, and training. Book your first appointment using Hound Hub in just 5 easy steps!

- To begin working with Hound Hub, activate the “Hound Hub” skill in your Alexa.
- Say or type “Open Hound Hub” to get started. Alexa will then list the services provided within Hound Hub.
- To learn more about which service you are interested in booking, state the name of the service. 
- Then, answer with whichever service you would like to book. Alexa will present you with the price details of your desired service.


Important!
Hound Hub is currently only compatible with Amazon Alexa.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
